pybg -- bondgeek's fixed income python libraries
================================================

pybg is a set of wrappers and extensions to QuantLib.  It is inspired by,
and borrows freely from Enthought's PyQL Cython wrappers for QuantLib.


Build Info
==========
    make build_ext
    make test


